 A MAN, Uchenna Egbuchulem, 47, has been arrested by police in Imo State for allegedly raping and impregnating his 17-year-old daughter. Egbuchulem, who hails from Nduhu Alaenyi in Mbaitoli council of the state, was said to have threatened to kill the teenager with a cutlass if she refused him. A village source said that after violating his blood daughter, the suspect kept taking advantage of her until she became pregnant. It was gathered that a medical doctor, to whom Egbuchulem reportedly wanted to sell the unborn baby, took the teen to the traditional ruler before whom the girl narrated what happened. Police spokeman Orlando Ikeokwu confirmed the incident, saying Egbuchulem had been taken into custody, while investigation continued.